Today, we join with millions of people around the world who mourn the loss of Nipsey Hussle. He often spoke and rapped about dedication. This video, produced by our team at The North Star, is all about Nipsey's dedication.

We hope you love and are inspired by it.

Thank you to all of the filmmakers and producers across the years whose footage is included here.
